# Cursor Indexing Exclusion
# Optimized to keep workspace under 500MB while retaining full context
# Excludes build artifacts, dependencies, media, and archives

# ============================================
# DEPENDENCIES & BUILD OUTPUTS (Largest savings)
# ============================================
# Node modules - massive and don't need indexing (~1.7GB)
**/node_modules/
node_modules/

# Build outputs - regenerated on build (~500MB+)
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
**/.expo/
**/out/
**/.turbo/
**/.vercel/
**/.cache/

# Lock files - not needed for code context
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml

# TypeScript build info
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# ============================================
# ARCHIVES & BACKUPS (~2GB+)
# ============================================
# All archives
**/*.zip
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.rar
**/*.7z
**/*.gz

# Backup directories
BUSINESS_APP_LATEST*/
CUSTOMER_APP_LATEST*/
canny-carrot-business-app-BACKUP*/
canny-carrot-business-app-fresh/
**/*BACKUP*/
**/*backup*/
**/*-BACKUP-*/

# Legacy/design directories (keep code, exclude assets)
canny-carrot-design-v1.2.1-full/
canny-carrot-design-v1.2.1b-full/
CannyCarrot_OfflineReady_v3.3_FullSuite/
Canny-carrot-website/
CC/
New folder/
rollback-v1.2.1a/

